{"type":null,"faqId":9534,"title":"荣耀X1（7D-501u）7.0   如何使用设备找回功能？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在遗忘或丢失荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">时，设备找回功能能够帮助您定位荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">当前所处的位置。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span></span><span style=\"color:#339966;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29976\" /></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">您的荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">需满足以下几个条件才可以使用设备找回功能：</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:6.5pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">是开机状态且已连接至互联网</span><span>;</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:6.5pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">已经在荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">上登录了华为帐号；</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">荣耀</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';font-size:10.5pt;\"> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">中<b>手机找回</b>功能已开启。您可以在主屏幕上点击<b>同步</b>，在<b>管控</b>区域开启<b>手机找回</b>功能</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>&nbsp;\n</p>\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29978\" /> \n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>1.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在</span><span> PC </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">端登录</span><span> www.hicloud.com</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，进入云服务首页。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>2.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在云服务首页点击<b>手机找回</b>，在弹出的对话框中输入云帐户密码即可在网页端管控您的荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">设备找回功能需要连接网络，定位成功后，在网页上会显示荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">当前所在的位置。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">您还可以远程向</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">发送警告信息、锁定</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、备份数据和清除数据等，以减少不必要的损失。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>&nbsp;\n</p>","faqTypeId":175,"faqType":"系统功能及设置","useful":3,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"136","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396255885000,"seriesProductName":"7D-501u","visitedTimes":748,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":5,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"找回","avgScore":5.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}